summary: Defines a container that gathers all objects defined in a Feast feature repository—such as entities, feature views, on‑demand views, stream views, feature services, permissions, and projects—and offers functionality to translate this collection into the Registry protobuf representation used by Feast.
business_intent: Enable serialization and export of a complete Feast repository's metadata so it can be stored, versioned, and deployed via the Feast registry infrastructure.
